27:16.320 --> 27:22.840
So actually, most of the human genome is made up of transposable elements that are usually

27:22.840 --> 27:26.720
kept silent all the time.

27:26.720 --> 27:33.240
And there's a few of them that are not silent, and they can still move around the genome.

27:33.240 --> 27:38.800
And when these are pieces of DNA, when they move around the genome, they're actually introducing

27:38.800 --> 27:41.240
mutations into the genome.

27:41.240 --> 27:47.640
