28:00.400 --> 28:04.160
So that would be really exciting to figure out that mechanism.

28:04.160 --> 28:11.240
And there were some early studies as well doing cross-species pro-nuclei transfers, so taking

28:11.240 --> 28:15.000
nuclei, putting it in another oocyte of a different species.

