And now my kids are going to be great at basketball.

40:27.560 --> 40:29.240
That's not necessarily going to be it.

40:29.240 --> 40:32.360
Exercise could cause endorphins, which may affect these systems.

40:32.360 --> 40:38.920
And then, you know, our children may have different stress responses in the brain, but

40:38.920 --> 40:40.840
it's not going to be everything that's inherited.

40:40.840 --> 40:43.200
And I think that that's important to keep in mind.

40:43.200 --> 40:49.800
And Lamarck was, you know, very careful in his theorizing, if you actually read what he

40:49.800 --> 40:56.360
